{"tid":2306534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢家係ig度tag#save12hkyouths 都會比人封ac","createTime":"2020-11-30T13:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T14:16:57.000Z","uid":210009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc94ef114531bc8382b811e8c89c0dc245e36861","tid":2306534,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"話說小弟條team個隊友前排<span class=\"red\">係壁仔拋完(還押)</span>，出返嚟決定<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">自己創業</span></span>，唔洗再比人欺壓又唔會咁容易比人取替到。於是佢就<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">開間ig舖幫人整動物標本</span></span>，姐係人地養魚養爬蟲養倉鼠養到死左但又想留佢副皮或者佢副骨留念之類果種。但係前排無啦啦比人<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">封左ac唔比佢落廣告。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9N75kG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9N75kG.png&h=f0bbc0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6qEWsn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6qEWsn.png&h=19fe8bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢明明呢段時間都冇出過新post新story，諗左幾終於知道係邊度踩度豬西伯格條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，原來係因為<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">個post同bio度都tag左</span></span><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">save12hkyouths</span></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrDCH7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrDCH7x.jpg&h=134496f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryhG9NA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryhG9NA.jpg&h=d57210d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隊友<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">灰撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>，白坐左十四日諗出嚟嘅創業之路一開波就比奶共伯格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩。<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">我都係本住幫得幾多得幾多同推動下本土藝術嘅心態幫佢出呢個post。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果你話乜都試晒發現真係冇市場都算，呢家廣告都唔比人落，佢之所以灰撚到喊係因為試都未試就被宣告失敗所以 <span class=\"x-large\">好 唔 甘 心 !</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">想請教下有冇人知可以點樣解返封比佢落廣告</span></span>(已經申訴左成個星期)或者有需要嘅人<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"large\">可以幫手follow下佢</span></span>，呢個係佢ig:<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/sangmit_st?igshid=2or553f6a27s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsangmit_st%3Figshid%3D2or553f6a27s&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=94c122d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/sangmit_st?igshid=2or553f6a27s</a></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\nPs:我有叫佢開<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">mewe</span></span>但唔知佢開成點。"},{"pid":"fdebe273639f53e85b676542beb3466e40a5f02f","tid":2306534,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d832452845d056e91d9bd1b9bafd54775a50dfc","tid":2306534,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0742b998d6455a314f5ff701e6363129bc4c8b","tid":2306534,"uid":122929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc94ef114531bc8382b811e8c89c0dc245e36861","tid":2306534,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"話說小弟條team個隊友前排<span class=\"red\">係壁仔拋完(還押)</span>，出返嚟決定<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">自己創業</span></span>，唔洗再比人欺壓又唔會咁容易比人取替到。於是佢就<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">開間ig舖幫人整動物標本</span></span>，姐係人地養魚養爬蟲養倉鼠養到死左但又想留佢副皮或者佢副骨留念之類果種。但係前排無啦啦比人<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">封左ac唔比佢落廣告。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9N75kG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%